//starting questions
Create var snooze time
If user runs program
Ask “Standard or military time?”
Ask “What time is your alarm?”

If user picked military
Loop every minute
Check military time if equal to alarm set then ring

Else 
Loop every minute
Check standard time if equal to alarm set then ring

//alarm rings
if alarm rings 
Ask “snooze”
Ask “stop” 

//snooze button
If user picked snooze
Set snooze time time+5 minutes

If time = snooze time 
Alarm ring 

//end button
If user picked stop 
End alarm
